    mu_2 = 0.687035170223597 (record #2, Aquiles, May 12 evening, worst pair (31, 38)),
    mu_3 = 0.687033937262633 (record #3, Boagrius, May 16 afternoon, worst pair (6, 17)),
    mu_4 = 0.687033931214091 (record #4, Boagrius, May 16 evening, worst pair (9, 25)).
    All verified byte-exact by 5 independent kernels per record.
    Previous Cohn record: 0.687160201509307. Cumulative improvement: -1.263e-4 absolute, -0.0184% relative.
